---
name: Cisco ISE → OCSF
description: |
  Maps parsed Cisco ISE events from the `cisco` topic to OCSF. Passed
  Authentications and Failed Attempts become OCSF Authentication events, RADIUS
  Accounting becomes OCSF Network Activity, and all other ISE categories become
  OCSF Base Events.
---

subscribe "cisco"
where @name.starts_with("cisco.ise.")
cisco::ise::ocsf::map
ocsf::derive
ocsf::cast
publish "ocsf"
